Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:04.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,When watching TV,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.59,0:00:06.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,please keep the room bright...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.08,0:00:08.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,...and sit well away from the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.26,0:00:09.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.00,0:00:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mistress Kuzuha, please reconsider \Nand give me a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.93,0:00:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Modernistic Cast Iron Top Toy Butler!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.36,0:00:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, me, the Cyborg Wheeled Insect Butler!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.56,0:00:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, me, the Mountain Bike Combat Butler!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.12,0:00:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, to tell the truth, \NI am a bit tired of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You can't mean that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.79,0:00:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sion, as I recall, our school's \Nculture fest is coming up, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.14,0:00:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Various groups are starting \Nto prepare their stalls as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.41,0:00:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like sweets shops.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.93,0:00:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it is time to go snack plundering!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.89,0:00:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.37,0:00:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One moment please!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.80,0:00:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, the second assassin of the "Mysterious \NButler – Non-Kids' Hobby Faction"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.05,0:00:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will defeat Hayate Ayasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.20,0:01:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not make me repeat myself. \NI said I have tired of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.84,0:01:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a gift I would very much like \Nto present to you, Mistress Kuzuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.69,0:01:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Those are from the cake shop featured \Non that Admatic show the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.54,0:01:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm, you are quite good. Do as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.68,0:01:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.84,0:01:23.06,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Whosoever commands the butlers, \Ncommands the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:28.48,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The Great Butler War that will \Nshake up the world has just begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.17,0:01:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Read it backwards or forwards, \N"KO-TO-KO" still reads as "KO-TO-KO"...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.12,0:01:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, we're not forming a band \Nor anything, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:37.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Zettai nante shinjinai!\NI don't believe in absolutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.98,0:01:40.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukanou nante nai!\NNo such thing as impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:45.95,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mirai wa hiraku te no naka ni aru\NThe future is in the open palm of my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.12,0:01:51.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Dou yattemo katenai akuma ga\NA demon that I just can't win against
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.46,0:01:56.25,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Megami no kao o shite chakkari (O_O;)\NBrazenly pretending to be a goddess (O_O;)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.96,0:02:01.80,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Keikenchi ja tannai kurai dakara\NExperience points are almost not enough
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.30,0:02:07.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Isshou tanren shikou-sakugo ni sessa-takuma\NTraining for life, working hard at trial and error
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.18,0:02:12.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mondai nara muzukashii-hodo ude ga naru shi\NTougher the problem the more it gets me going
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.23,0:02:17.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Yorokobu kao ga mirerya sore de ii shi\NSeeing the joy on your face is enough for me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.48,0:02:23.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Takara no chizu o boku wa te ni ireta\NI've found a treasure map
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:29.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Juuou-mujin kimi o tsurete tsuki-susumou!\NTotally free, I'll take you and push forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.91,0:02:32.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Happii na kanchigai\NA happy misunderstanding
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.50,0:02:35.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Chikai wa yuruganai!\NMy pledge will stand fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:40.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaze no yukue mo kaete-miseru\NI'll even change the direction of the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.84,0:02:43.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakkou wa kini-shinai\NI won't care how I look
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.35,0:02:46.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Unmei ja kujikenai!\NNo destiny will discourage me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.39,0:02:51.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Ano kumo chirasu hayate no gotoku!\NLike the sudden gale scattering the clouds!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.74,0:03:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! Academy Culture Fest – Part 1
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's done! I managed to \Nfinish it just in time somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:18.80,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,2007 Hakuou Academy Culture Fest
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.18,0:03:20.10,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.10,0:03:23.36,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I am definitely getting back \Nto the estate to see the Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.74,0:03:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Hayata, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.13,0:03:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The school building is that way, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.63,0:03:28.43,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.89,0:03:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Festival loving Miss \NCommittee Chairman, Red!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.54,0:03:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Chairman, Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.12,0:03:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disciplinary committee member, Black!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Together, the three of us are...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the student body council!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.77,0:03:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come shake our hands \Nat the culture fest hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.86,0:03:44.24,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.08,0:03:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.40,0:03:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined you would really \Ncomplete the arch overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.75,0:03:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it was worth it for us to twiddle \Nour thumbs until the last minute
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.81,0:03:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before we begged you for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:04:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we hadn't made it on time, we \Nwould've gotten a real earful from Hina.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.42,0:04:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm glad we were able to \Nsalvage the situation somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to get going now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.13,0:04:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.09,0:04:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still need you to do \Nwork in the classroom, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.78,0:04:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We feel bad for making you work hard alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.83,0:04:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the least we can do \Nto make up for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.44,0:04:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us sweat by your side together!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:26.32,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Senzu Beans
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.20,0:04:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Here you are! \NIt's to thank you for the arch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.74,0:04:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're really, really counting on you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then shall we hurry along?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should get ready to open shop soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.06,0:04:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.09,0:04:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Hayata for you. So understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.44,0:04:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Away we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.97,0:04:46.65,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,2007 Hakuou Academy Culture Fest
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.78,0:04:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Nagi, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:51.02,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Yonday
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:52.02,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical Destroy \NNagi Sanzenin
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:53.68,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical Destroy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.05,0:04:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it obvious? It's a solo culture fest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:03.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I think her interpretation \Nof "culture" is a bit off...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that reminds me. Hakuou Academy's \Nculture fest starts today, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.63,0:05:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Hayate had to \Nstay overnight again last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.63,0:05:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it appears that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.65,0:05:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I expect he's had a ton \Nof work foisted off on him,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because he's unable to say "no".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.19,0:05:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear! He should only be so good-natured!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.10,0:05:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate's supposed to be {\i1}my{\i0} butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.41,0:05:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He shouldn't work so hard for everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:27.80,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it bothers you that much, \Nwhy don't you go to the culture fest?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?! I-It's not really bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.34,0:05:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate crowds anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.16,0:05:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear Hayate is doing \Na cosplay café with the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I imagine he's doing \Na splendid job about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.05,0:05:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A c-cosplay café, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:51.87,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Customer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.38,0:05:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? An order? I despair of this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher! I mean, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.28,0:05:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"No, no, I'm still far from it."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.45,0:06:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no helping it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.68,0:06:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're that worried \Nabout Hayate's safety...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I will go myself \Nand do a bit of scouting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call the SP. I'll be leaving \Nas soon as I get changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.21,0:06:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi still has such a childish side to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.03,0:06:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, perhaps that is not so true...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.12,0:06:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:32.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The Hakuou Academy culture fest: \Na gigantic event held once every year
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.81,0:06:35.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,that is a specialty of Ward S \Nin the Metropolitan area.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.07,0:06:37.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, it's a super prestigious school,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.69,0:06:40.29,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,so an endless roster of \Npoliticians, businessmen,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:42.85,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and distinguished people \Nfrom all walks of life come to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.85,0:06:45.32,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Surpassing the scope \Nof a simple school festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:48.28,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,they get fabulous guests \Nparticipating as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:51.77,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, the level of their \Nresearch presentations is so high,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.77,0:06:54.76,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,even industrial spies and intelligence \Nagencies from various countries
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:57.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,supposedly quietly take note.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:01.52,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,KA-BOOM
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.68,0:07:04.77,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a totally cultural \Nand festive three days!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Might I ask for another \Ncup of royal milk tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.90,0:07:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly. Please wait a moment, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.41,0:07:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, how may I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you there, bring us \Nmore tea over here as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the double, in a pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.90,0:07:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Um, you three, why are you \Nplaying a leisurely game of cards?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.08,0:07:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you are just so brisk \Nand alert, we cannot keep up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.88,0:07:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revolution!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.23,0:07:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We feel kind of bad \Ngetting in the way of a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.65,0:07:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Counterrevolution!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.28,0:07:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't say that! Please work!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, this isn't a cosplay \Ncafé. It's a butler café.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.93,0:07:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But we {\i1}are{\i0} in costumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, could it be that you planned \Nto make me handle everything
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that's why you made it a butler café?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.93,0:08:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot say I approve \Nof such paranoia, Hayata.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-All right, now that we've recharged, \Nshall we get serious now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.72,0:08:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.79,0:08:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your hard work, Hayata. \NYou can rest for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.37,0:08:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'm going to \Nmake a run back to the estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayasaki, are you here?! \NYou're here, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.12,0:08:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Miss Katsura...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.01,0:08:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.12,0:08:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...COME!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.82,0:08:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Little Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.47,0:08:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there, Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.72,0:08:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have you know, it's not like I came \Nbecause I wanted to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.57,0:08:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only here because Maria asked me \Nto come check on things...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.18,0:08:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's Hayata, he's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.97,0:08:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got taken away by Yukiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.47,0:08:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Hayate's not here?! \NAfter I came all this way to see him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.01,0:08:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Superintendent does not appear \Nto be making any unusual moves at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.87,0:08:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that. But don't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.88,0:09:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given this rowdy atmosphere, \Nthere's no way she's going to behave...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayasaki, what about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.70,0:09:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do this with that, and this \Nwith that! Omitting the rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.85,0:09:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get it stamped at HQ, on the double!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayasaki, you know, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.84,0:09:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only have 500 yen right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.97,0:09:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but between octopus balls and a \NJapanese pizza, which should I buy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.46,0:09:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.72,0:09:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Hayate managing things \Nhere for all he's worth?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.28,0:09:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's your job as the \Nadvising teacher, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.52,0:09:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't really know how \Nto answer all the questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.03,0:09:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.81,0:09:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:10:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruko, can I ask you to handle things here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.84,0:10:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, come with me for a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? But I'm still in the middle \Nof giving instructions...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.29,0:10:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Miss Harukaze, this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.33,0:10:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make the judgment call yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.97,0:10:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That will not be recognized as an expense!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:18.09,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Receipt
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.12,0:10:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.39,0:10:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's thanks for taking care of my officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.37,0:10:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.26,0:10:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's written all over \Nyour face that you're hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine that you're good-natured,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.13,0:10:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you're going to collapse \Nif you push yourself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinagiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.02,0:10:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hayate?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.56,0:10:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.08,0:10:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Jör? Try not to \Neat stuff off the ground too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.83,0:10:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Superintendent!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:58.51,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:11:01.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And in the meantime, Mademoiselle Nagi was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh! That Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.45,0:11:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he? And what is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.04,0:11:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SPs, split up and look for Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.88,0:11:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired, so I'm going to stay here and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.54,0:11:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh? Hey! Everyone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.76,0:11:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:29.30,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, you jerk...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.30,0:11:32.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,After I took the plunge \Nto leave the residence, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.09,0:11:34.51,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.51,0:11:38.16,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to walk around \Nand see the festival with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.16,0:11:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You there, the young lady \Nwith the pigtails...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.13,0:11:44.26,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortune Telling
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.13,0:11:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you would like, why \Ndon't you drop by for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:49.14,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortune Telling
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.48,0:11:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no use for scams.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.14,0:11:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.18,0:11:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My fortunes are 100 accurate, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.22,0:11:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.36,0:12:01.19,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Compatibility Fortunes \NSuper specialized in mistress-butler relations!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.15,0:12:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.69,0:12:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll kill a little time \Nwhile I take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.95,0:12:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't be bad to reconfirm \Nthe strength of my bond with Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.84,0:12:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then first, please look deep into my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.68,0:12:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... I can see... into your forlorn heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will help myself to the opening \Nin your heart and take advantage of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.71,0:12:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll listen to you, just once...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi Sanzenin, you \Nare now my just-once puppet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.66,0:13:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet potatoes! Roasted sweet potatoes!\N({\u1}I{\u0}shi-yaki imo! Oi{\u1}mo{\u0}!)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.14,0:13:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, honestly, just a little, okay?\N({\u1}Mo{\u0}u, chotto dake {\u1}yo{\u0}?)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.63,0:13:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.28,0:13:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here's a souvenir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.93,0:13:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were immersed in Jör's \Ndigestive fluids and you are still fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Jör?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.35,0:13:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jörmungandr. That is his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.46,0:13:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His favorite foods are the five lands, \Nthree seas, and all living things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.33,0:13:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He really enjoys butlers in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.22,0:13:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.82,0:13:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since this is a time slot \Nthat is supposed to cater to youths.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.23,0:13:42.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,But that didn't seem like a joke to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:44.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And what is up with \Nthat suspicious-looking outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.71,0:13:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Superintendent, what \Nare you plotting out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.01,0:13:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. I am simply off duty right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.34,0:13:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahem! Simply off duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, I would not object, \Nif someone were to entertain me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me, boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.17,0:14:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you spurned your prize of \N100 school credits from the butler battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.94,0:14:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.12,0:14:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? That was, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.26,0:14:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't really have a need for it
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.27,0:14:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a-and from an education stand point, \Nit wouldn't have been good for the Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Miss"!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Miss"! "Miss"!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.52,0:14:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the "Miss" the only thing \Nthat you have in your life?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.34,0:14:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.91,0:14:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a duller man than I had thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough already! \NLet us forget about this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.66,0:14:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.65,0:14:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.66,0:14:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, you wouldn't happen to be \Nwith Nagi, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Does that mean \Nthe Miss is here at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, she should've \Narrived quite a while ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it seems she forgot her cell phone
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.16,0:14:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and so I tried to get in touch \Nwith the members of the SP, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.99,0:14:54.28,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to believe
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:57.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Power of flower
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:15:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erina, you're the best. \NYou're the best. You're the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:15:01.60,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,With arms wide open
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.87,0:15:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erina, you're the best. You're the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:03.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Like giving a tight hug...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong, Hayate?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.78,0:15:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, it seems the Miss has gone missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been right there for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.97,0:15:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.54,0:15:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.28,0:15:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.87,0:15:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, there's somewhere I want you \Nto come with me for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.81,0:15:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, there's somewhere I want you \Nto come with me for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.39,0:15:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-There clearly seems to be \Nsomething serious going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.89,0:15:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.48,0:15:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I have something urgent \Nto attend to now, so excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.97,0:15:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I'll come, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.02,0:15:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Mistress Kuzuha, \Ncould that possibly be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hm, it is his doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.23,0:15:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has done better than expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.41,0:15:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is getting interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.33,0:15:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are going after them, Sion!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.67,0:15:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my blood sugar level is still...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.04,0:15:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mistress Kuzuha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:16:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, there's somewhere I want you \Nto accompany me for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.61,0:16:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you look at it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.78,0:16:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she's in that hypnotic state \Nyou see a lot in manga and stuff, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.44,0:16:15.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who did this, \Nbut how dare they do this to the Miss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.82,0:16:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she stopped for some reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, all that aside,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:23.00,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Japanese Pizza
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.90,0:16:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to try some of this food with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.66,0:16:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me, I'd like one, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:28.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! It's tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is she really hypnotized?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.67,0:16:32.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,With the bewildered pair in tow,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.81,0:16:35.76,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Nagi aimlessly paraded \Nall over the academy and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.24,0:16:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.47,0:16:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nor here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.72,0:16:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nor here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.27,0:16:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nor here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nor here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:46.65,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(99,91)}{sign}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nor here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nor is it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.07,0:16:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is the place. \NThis is where I wanted to bring you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is the old school building?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.17,0:16:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why didn't you \Nbring us here to begin with?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.07,0:17:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I let you manipulate me just once!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.08,0:17:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your hard work, Nagi Sanzenin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.62,0:17:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did well to follow my order \Nand lure Hayate Ayasaki out for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.31,0:17:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, does this count as being "lured out"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That outfit... Could it be that you're...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.25,0:17:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They call me the Mysterious Butler \Nof Darkness, Just-Once Puppeteer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.49,0:17:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's just exactly what you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.53,0:17:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what in the world is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, please snap out of it! \NIt's me! It's Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.44,0:17:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, I wanted to see \Nthe festival together with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.85,0:17:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no fun being alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:43.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.48,0:17:45.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.53,0:17:48.43,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to catch that guy quickly \Nand make him undo the hypnosis!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.47,0:17:58.22,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,This Week's Butler Battle
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.34,0:17:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.55,0:17:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A robot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.97,0:18:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate Ayasaki, I will defeat you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.87,0:18:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and restore our mistress's \Nfaith in us, without fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is this?! H-How big is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.85,0:18:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sis?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, I'll handle that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.65,0:18:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look after Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.94,0:18:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, uh, where did \Nthat bamboo sword come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.96,0:18:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who disturbs the academy's \Npeace has to answer to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't tell me you mean to fight \Nthe robot with a bamboo sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.54,0:18:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn! Scurrying all over the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.31,0:18:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Head!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.56,0:18:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This girl got the camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.88,0:18:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Firing anchor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.74,0:18:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hinagiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.38,0:19:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.41,0:19:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.29,0:19:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, that hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.86,0:19:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinagiku, please don't be so reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.16,0:19:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I just found him unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.38,0:19:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, give up the fight \Nand come on out quietly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.25,0:19:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will now expect you \Nto undo the Miss's hypnosis!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.97,0:19:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In your dreams. The fight is just beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.31,0:19:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will destroy Hakuou Academy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:49.79,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Warning
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.59,0:19:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot! The sparks and firing \Nthe jet have affected the adhesive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.46,0:20:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.31,0:20:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.27,0:20:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.70,0:20:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.33,0:20:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.24,0:20:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear, that Hayate... \NIt is no fun alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.63,0:20:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To hell with the culture fest...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.68,0:20:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I absolutely hate this culture fest!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.34,0:20:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.36,0:20:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she still hypnotized?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.00,0:20:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the queen of the true culture of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.78,0:20:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.49,0:20:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will show you what true culture is!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.35,0:20:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-True...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.99,0:20:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...culture?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.98,0:20:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.89,0:20:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It does not just belong \Nin the summer and winter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.65,0:20:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Autumn is the season \Nfor festivals to begin with!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.50,0:21:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Autumn should have a new \NJapanese culture festival as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.85,0:21:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is quite interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.92,0:21:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Superintendent!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.50,0:21:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi Sanzenin, was it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.47,0:21:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are far more promising \Nthan that butler boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.83,0:21:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.66,0:21:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would love for you to show me \Nthis true festival of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.30,0:21:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.67,0:21:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.11,0:21:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.92,0:21:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not follow me. I do not need dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.46,0:21:29.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And make sure you record \Nthat late night show.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.99,0:21:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.47,0:21:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is that really hypnosis?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.68,0:21:35.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, a new culture fest will be held.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.52,0:21:38.40,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all people, they will be \Nfighting Miss Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.40,0:21:39.90,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.69,0:21:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the boiled egg...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.21,0:21:51.74,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,They were in the midst \Nof their sports fest today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.37,0:21:54.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Waratte lun-lun-lun\NSmile lun-lun-lun
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.37,0:21:58.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Lala-lun-lun-lulu naita hi mo\NLala-lun-lun-lulu even on a day I've cried
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.17,0:22:03.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawagu kaze ni yureru egao kokoro hareteku\NA smile wavers in the wind and clears my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.84,0:22:07.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyou mo lun-lun-lun mawarun-lun-lulu\NToday again lun-lun-lun turning lun-lun-lulu
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.05,0:22:18.31,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiyou no shita de kimi to odoru kimagure na dansu\NA whimsical dance with you under the sun
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.73,0:22:26.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanige-naku sashi-dasu te ni mitorete\NRiveted by the hand you've casually offered
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.61,0:22:32.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugi no kotoba maigo ni natchau no\NMy next words become lost
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.91,0:22:37.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonabite tsutsumi-komu manazashi ni\NThe mature gaze that envelopes me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.04,0:22:42.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuyogari wasurete-yuku\NMakes me forget my bravado
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.46,0:22:49.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Sotto furetete nemurenai yoru no nagai toki mo\NKeep that soft touch on long sleepless nights
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.72,0:22:54.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Yume kara sameta bakari no hoho ni mo\NAnd on my cheek, just awakened from a dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.56,0:22:56.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Lun-lun-lun\NLun-lun-lun
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.47,0:23:00.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Lala-lun-lun-lulu tsun to shita\NLala-lun-lun-lulu that hoity profile
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.86,0:23:05.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Yokogao hora atto iu ma waratteru desho?\NLook, there's a smile there already, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.98,0:23:09.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora to lun-lun-lun mawarun-lun-lulu\NWith the sky lun-lun-lun turning lun-lun-lulu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.24,0:23:13.70,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi ga fukasu kaze no naka\NIn a breeze of your making
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.70,0:23:20.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Odoru hidamari no dansu\NA dance in a sunny spot
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.21,0:23:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.05,0:23:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Hayate...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.96,0:23:28.92,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(224,46)}Ayumu Nishizawa's
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.96,0:23:28.92,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(207,288)}Lettering by Mikako Takahashi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.96,0:23:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Ayumu Nishizawa's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.92,0:23:30.55,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Butler Report
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.23,0:23:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Butler Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.25,0:23:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit Transformation! I am Nagi Sanzenin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.55,0:23:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Hayate Ayasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.84,0:23:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Ayumu Nishizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.18,0:23:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let us get right to the long-awaited \Nfan service shot of the hamster.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.06,0:23:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this is exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.61,0:23:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.44,0:23:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a powerful photo taken \Nat a certain ramen shop in Suginami Ward.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.44,0:23:47.73,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\pos(16,15)}Super Big Bowl \NFinish the Ramen and It's Free!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.24,0:23:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will she finish eating it in time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.92,0:23:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's truly a photo about pushing the limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.73,0:23:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, no fair. Boohoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.87,0:23:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's very like you, \Nso I think it's good in its way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.82,0:23:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.45,0:23:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.16,0:23:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,224)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.20,0:23:59.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, this is the Hakuou Academy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.16,0:24:16.55,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(174,307)}The next episode of \N"Hayate the Combat Butler" is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.75,0:24:01.80,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Right? Don't you think \Nit's a weird building?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.80,0:24:04.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As of now, we will vend \NNagi Sanzenin's doujinshi
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.34,0:24:06.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,at a specially prepared \Nbooth in the Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.74,0:24:11.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayasaki, if your doujinshi wins \Nagainst ours by selling better...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.13,0:24:13.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, this \Nis a doujinshi sales competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.91,0:24:16.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way my manga \Nwill lose against you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.55,0:24:17.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on "Hayate the Combat Butler",
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.93,0:24:20.25,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Why Dead?! Academy Culture Fest – Part 2".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.10,0:24:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Hayate the Combat Butler \NWhy Dead?! Academy Culture Fest – Part 2
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.25,0:24:21.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.06,0:24:23.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,At the world's largest doujinshi fair venue,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.46,0:24:25.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,it's hard to get through on your cell phone.
